{"article_id":"n9ZAHmpY1V3bcJam","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Top Clinton campaign officials urged FBI Director James Comey on Sunday to provide more details about the bureau 's review of newly-discovered emails","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"related to the investigation of Hillary Clinton 's use of a private server ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"charging","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that his `` inappropriate '' letter","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"announcing the review Friday","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"is fueling conspiracy theories","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"that could hurt the Democratic nominee just days before the election .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"Clinton campaign chairman John Podesta ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"appearing on CNN 's State of the Union with Jake Tapper ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"called the letter","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"released by Comey on Friday","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"`` long on innuendo , short on facts , ''","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"noting","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that Comey could not even say","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"if the emails contained significant information .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Comey appeared to be breaking with precedent","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"by disclosing information about an ongoing investigation","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"before determining","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"if the newly-discovered emails provide any new insights ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Podesta said .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"`` If they 're not significant ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"they 're not significant , ''","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"said Podesta ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"who called Comey 's action `` inappropriate . ''","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"He added","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that Comey `` should have read them first ''","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"before making a bombshell announcement about the emails just 11 days before the election .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"`` This is something","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"that has been tossed into the middle of the campaign , ''","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Podesta said .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"We would have preferred","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that that not happen ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"but","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"now that it has happened ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"we would prefer","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"that Mr. Comey come forward","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and explain","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"why he took that unprecedented step . ''","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Attorney General Loretta Lynch objected to Comey 's decision","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"to announce the probe ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"according to Justice Department sources ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"because she felt","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"it violated department policy","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"to not takes step","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"that may interfere with an election .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Attorney General Lynch objected to FBI director going public with email review","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"FBI obtains warrant","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"to review emails","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"linked to Huma Abedin","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Clinton campaign manager Robby Mook said","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"he does n't believe","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Comey 's action will cost Clinton the election .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"`` I do n't think so , ''","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Mook said on NBC 's Meet the Press ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"adding","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"that Clinton is gaining an `` insurmountable lead '' in the swing state of Nevada .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"But Mook urged Comey to put more information about the emails `` out there on the table .","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"'' If Comey does n't do that ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Mook said ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"the FBI director will end up fueling conspiracy theories .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"`` Let 's just get all the information out there","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"so that rumors and hypotheticals can be put to rest , ''","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Mook said .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"Donald Trump tweeted Sunday","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"that Democratic criticism of Comey is hypocritical .","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"Trump running mate Mike Pence praised the FBI 's decision","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"to review the emails ,","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"but sent an ambiguous message","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"about how it might affect the election .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"it alters the campaign at all , \"","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Pence told Fox News Sunday .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"\" What we already know here is troubling to the American people ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"and it ' s convincing millions of Americans","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"that Hillary Clinton is just a risky choice in this election . \"","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Democratic vice presidential nominee Tim Kaine called Comey 's letter `` extremely puzzling '' and a `` distraction '' in an interview with ABC News ' This Week .","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"Comey sent a letter to congressional leaders on Friday","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"announcing","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"that newly discovered emails were being reviewed in connection with the investigation of Clinton 's use of a private email server while secretary of state .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"The emails were found during a separate investigation of former Congressman Anthony Weiner , the estranged husband of Huma Abedin , a longtime Clinton aide and adviser .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"Weiner is suspected of having sexually explicit communications with a 15-year-old girl . `` It is just extremely puzzling , \"","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"Kaine said .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"\" Why would you release information","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"that is so incomplete","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"when you haven ' t even seen the material yourself ?","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Eleven days before an election , why would you talk about an ongoing investigation ?","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"I just have no way","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"of understanding these actions .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"They ' re completely unprecedented .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"And that ' s why I think","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"( Comey ) owes the American public more information . ''","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"Kaine added","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"that , `` As far as we know now ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Director Comey knows nothing about the content of these emails .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"We don ' t know","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"whether they ' re to or from Hillary at all . ''","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"Podesta said","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Abedin has been fully cooperating with the FBI .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"He also said","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"she remains on the campaign staff .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Trump campaign manager Kellyanne Conway praised Comey 's decision","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"to announce the review of the newly found emails .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"`` Hillary Clinton flouted the law","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"and set up a private server","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"so she could hide stuff from the public , ''","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"Conway said .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"Sen. Ron Johnson , R-Wis. , chairman of the Senate Homeland Security and Governmental Affairs Committee , said ,","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"`` I 'm not praising James Comey . ''","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"`` I think","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"this investigation has been bungled from the start , ''","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"the senator said on Fox News .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"Rep. Adam Schiff of California , the senior Democrat on the House Intelligence Committee , called it `` a terrible error in judgement by","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"( Comey )","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"to release this kind of ambiguous letter . ''","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"`` If the director ca n't clean up this mess ,","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"and I hope","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"he will try ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"I think","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"he ought to acknowledge","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"that he made a serious mistake ,","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"and underscore once again","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"that there 's nothing","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"that alters that core conclusion","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"he reached in July , ''","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"Schiff said on ABC 's This Week .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"He was referring to Comey 's previous announcement","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"that Clinton had been `` extremely careless ''","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"in using a private server","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"but had committed no crime .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":259,"left":0,"right":258,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":258,"left":192,"right":257,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":192,"left":178,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":167,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":144,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":136,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":131,"right":135,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":3,"right":134,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":134,"left":132,"right":133,"relation":"same-unit","nu